*** story ***
once upon a time a forest there lived a monkey who resided on berry tree which was on a bank of a river in the same forest
there lived a crocodile and his wife one day the crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under teh tree
and the kind hearted monkey offerd him some fruits the crocodile came back to the next day for more fruits
as he loves them as days passed by the crocodile and the monkey became good freinds
